# CODEOWNERS - Architecture Refactoring Project
#
# This file defines code ownership for the architecture refactoring components.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull
# request that modifies code they own.
#
# Format: <path/pattern> @username @org/team-name
#
# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

