# =============================================================================
# Notes for Maintainers
# =============================================================================
#
# Team Aliases (configure in GitHub Organization settings):
#   @architecture-team - Core architecture and refactoring specialists
#   @qa-team - Quality assurance and testing specialists
#   @devops-team - CI/CD and infrastructure specialists
#
# Review Requirements:
#   - All PRs modifying owned files require approval from at least one code owner
#   - Branch protection rules enforce code owner reviews
#   - See .github/BRANCH_PROTECTION.md for complete requirements
#
# Emergency Bypass:
#   - Only administrators can bypass code owner review requirements
#   - Use emergency rollback via feature flags instead (see BRANCH_PROTECTION.md)
#
# Adding New Owners:
#   1. Update this file with new ownership rules
#   2. Ensure team aliases exist in GitHub Organization settings
#   3. Test by creating a PR that modifies owned files
#   4. Verify correct owners are auto-requested for review
#
